# HR Analytics and Employee Data Management using SQL

## 📌 Project Overview
This project focuses on analyzing an HR database using SQL. It includes employee, department, and job-related data to generate meaningful insights.

## 🛠 Tools Used
- MySQL 
- HR Sample Database

## 📂 Project Structure
- hr databse.sql → Table creation scripts
- queries.sql → SQL queries for analysis

## 🔍 Key Analysis Performed
- Employee salary analysis
- Department-wise employee distribution
- Job history tracking
- Highest and second-highest salary queries
- Aggregate functions (SUM, AVG, COUNT)

## 🚀 Key Concepts Used
- Joins (INNER, LEFT)
- Subqueries
- Group By & Having
- Aggregate Functions

## 📊 Sample Insights
- Identified top-paid employees
- Department with highest number of employees
- Salary trends across departments

